flowRoot.flowPara: Data is necessary for research. Only with data can you make discoveries. You can collect data by clicking on your detector. Once you hire students, they will also collect data for you.
In Particle Clicker, you can research many interesting particles.
Every time your lab researches something, it becomes more popular. This "reputation" guarantees you a contant stream of funding in form of "jetons" (JTN), the coins used for buying coffee at CERN.

PhD students, Postdocs, Professors and maybe more are the types of workers you can hire in Particle Clicker to make your academic life easier. The will ease the tedious task of collecting data for you so you can focus on your research.
